MTN has launched a post-paid promotion which will double certain contract values. The Twice Your Value promotion will double the inclusive data, SMS, and MTN-to-MTN minutes post-paid subscribers receive on their packages, said MTN. This promotion is valid from 21 April to 31 May. Qualifying customers will receive 100% value back every month for three months of their contract. The Twice Your Value promotion is available on: Customers who sign up or upgrade on a qualifying tariff plan with an LTE device will also receive a 30GB once-off data bundle.